{
  "uid": "v12-1-alert-rule-page",
  "title": "Grafana 12.1 \u2014 New Alert Rule Page (GA)",
  "description": "The Alert rule authoring page went GA in 12.1 (guided wizard, simplified routing, recording-rule parity). This demo shows live alert counts + links to the new UI.",
  "tags": [
    "grafana-12",
    "v12.1",
    "alerting",
    "v12-demo"
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 40,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-30m",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {},
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "ds_prom",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "current": {
          "text": "Prometheus",
          "value": "prom"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 10000,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "tags": [
        "demo-guide"
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<div style=\"padding:1.2rem;background:#1a2a3a;border-left:4px solid #5794f2;border-radius:6px;font-family:system-ui\"><div style=\"font-size:.75rem;letter-spacing:.18em;color:#8aa9d0;margin-bottom:.3rem\">DEMO GUIDE</div><div style=\"font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:600;color:#fff;margin-bottom:.6rem\">Grafana 12.1 \u2014 New Alert Rule Page (GA)</div><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem\"><div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#5794f2;margin-bottom:.2rem\">\ud83c\udfaf What you're looking at</div><div style=\"font-size:.88rem;color:#dfe7f0\">The Alert Rule authoring page went GA in 12.1. Guided wizard, simplified routing, recording-rule parity.</div></div><div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#73bf69;margin-bottom:.2rem\">\ud83e\uddea Try this</div><div style=\"font-size:.88rem;color:#dfe7f0\">Click the link to /alerting/new/alerting and walk through the wizard.</div></div></div><div style=\"margin-top:.8rem;padding-top:.6rem;border-top:1px solid #2d3e54;font-size:.85rem\">\ud83d\udcda <strong style=\"color:#fff\">Learn more</strong>: <a href=\"https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/alerting/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#ff9830\">Grafana docs</a> \u00b7 <a href=\"https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/whatsnew/whats-new-in-v12-1/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#ff9830\">v12 What's New</a></div></div>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 16,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### What changed\n\n12.1 moved the **Alert rule page** out of preview. You now get:\n\n- A guided wizard for Grafana-managed alert rules (& recording rules from 12.0)\n- Simpler *Notifications* step with step-mode routing\n- Inline preview of the alert expression\n- Parity with Prometheus-managed rules via `grafanaManagedRecordingRules`\n\n### Try it\n\n- [\u27a1 Create a new alert rule](/alerting/new/alerting)\n- [\u27a1 Create a new recording rule](/alerting/new/recording)\n- [\u27a1 Alert rule list](/alerting/list)\n- [\u27a1 Contact points](/alerting/notifications)\n\n### Suggested recipe\n\n```\nName:       grafana:api_p95_breach\nExpression: histogram_quantile(0.95,\n              sum by (le)(rate(grafana_http_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m]))\n            ) > 0.5\nFor:        5m\nLabels:     severity=warning, service=grafana\n```"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Alert rules",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 16,
        "y": 7
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_prom}",
        "type": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(grafana_alerting_rule_group_rules) or on() vector(0)"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "description": "Alert rules. Reference: https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/alerting/"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Rules evaluating",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 16,
        "y": 11
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_prom}",
        "type": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "rate(grafana_alerting_rule_evaluations_total[$__rate_interval]) or on() vector(0)"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "decimals": 3
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "description": "Rules evaluating. Reference: https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/alerting/"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Rule evaluation duration (p95)",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 10,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 15
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_prom}",
        "type": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le)(rate(grafana_alerting_rule_evaluation_duration_seconds_bucket[$__rate_interval]))) or on() vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "p95"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "decimals": 4,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "lineWidth": 2
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "showLegend": false
        }
      },
      "description": "Rule evaluation duration (p95). Reference: https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/alerting/"
    }
  ]
}